name: Harry Styles
description:
Harry Edward Styles (born 1 February 1994) is an English singer and songwriter. His musical career began in 2010 as a solo contestant on the British music competition series The X Factor. Following his elimination, he was brought back to join the boy band One Direction. It became one of the best-selling boy groups of all time before going on an indefinite hiatus in 2016.

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon! It will support my work. Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here! If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Hey everyone! Nice to see you all again! Today I want to introduce a textual inversion of Harry Styles! I used 30 public images of him with an 9000 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add harstyles94 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20/30, and CFG between 7 and 7.5 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras. Both Edge Of Realism and Realistic Vision are able to give you good results;
